            "title": "29歲男持六合彩聲稱中頭獎到馬會領獎不果 死纏爛打拒走馬會報警求助",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/bf3de6faee22c0aa3f91a259eeef9b96/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250204/_2025020414012554762.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>年初五（2日）六合彩新春金多寶攪珠結果出爐，今期金多寶頭獎彩金是史上最高，結果一注獨中派逾1.93億元破紀錄。一名29歲姓洪男子，今（4日）早上11時56分，到跑馬地香港賽馬會總部大樓，手持一張六合彩彩票聲稱自己中「頭獎」，要求取得獎金，但經職員核對，證實事主並無得獎，事主卻不肯離開，仍多番糾纏，職員無奈報警求助。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4058601/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"男子聲稱六合彩中頭獎到馬會總部領獎不果拒走。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f944ae6bf111c25dd7a8140ae839c688/2025-02/0b171e9f-f0e3-4da1-859b-6a432e5d522c.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        男子聲稱六合彩中頭獎到馬會總部領獎不果拒走。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4058602/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"馬會職員報警求助。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/00a1ed95e3aa1ffd40a53fd06a2d72a5/2025-02/e9cf1783-d691-4c9c-bb2b-470d9ad93763.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        馬會職員報警求助。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>警員接報到場，經過一輪解釋後，事主同意離開，警方將案件列作誤會。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
